text: Novotaymasovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Taymasovsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 579 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Yermolayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Novotaymasovo
